        "expandedUncertainty": 0.082,
        "description": "Experimental comparison uncertainty accounts for measurement repeatability (CV 4.1%), inter-laboratory variability from FDA round-robin data, and CFD boundary condition uncertainty propagated via 500-sample Monte Carlo. Combined expanded uncertainty at 95% confidence is 8.2% of mean NIH."
