      "description": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver kernel. Observed order of accuracy for velocity components is 1.97 (expected 2.0 for second-order scheme), confirming correct implementation. Residual convergence to 1e-6 achieved for all operating points. No hasUncertaintyQuantification attached to this result as solver verification is treated as a pass/fail code-quality check under MRL 2 practice; formal UQ bounds are not required for this activity per internal SOP V-CFD-003.",
