    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Experimental comparison MARE of 8.2% satisfies the 15% acceptance criterion. GCI discretization uncertainty of 3.7% satisfies the 5% criterion. Model form sensitivity within acceptable bounds. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the defined COU. Decision: Accepted.",
